def DY_Analyz(dt,fetlst,cls):
    for f in fetlst:
        pandas.crosstab(dt[f],dt[cls]).plot(kind='barh',figsize=(8,4),color=["g","m"])
        mtpl.title('Intrusive Attacks by {}'.format(f), fontsize=15,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.xlabel('{}'.format(f), fontsize=12,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.ylabel('Count', fontsize=12,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.grid()
        mtpl.show()

def NumFetVZ(dtlst,ftlst,trg,usc):
    for fl in ftlst:
        avgs=[]
        for dl in dtlst:
            avgs.append(dl[fl].mean())
        mtpl.figure(figsize=(7,3))
        mtpl.title('Analysis of {}'.format(fl), fontsize=15,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.bar(usc,avgs,alpha=0.5,width=0.7,color=["#7FE817","#00008B","#FD1C03"])
        mtpl.xlabel('{}'.format(fl), fontsize=12,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.ylabel('Average', fontsize=12,color='#045F5F')
        mtpl.grid()
        mtpl.show()

def EncData(dt,catfets):
    dt_enc=dt.copy()
    for of in range(len(catfets)):
        dt_enc[catfets[of]]=dt_enc[catfets[of]].replace(dt_enc[catfets[of]].unique(),[i+1 for i in range(len(dt_enc[catfets[of]].unique()))])
    dt_enc.info()
    return dt_enc

def AttrSet(X_train,y_train):
    nmattr=X_train.columns.tolist()
    mdlattr = ensemble.RandomForestClassifier(random_state=0)
    mdlattr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    attr_imp = mdlattr.feature_importances_
    df_attr_sel=pandas.DataFrame({"Feature":nmattr,"Importance":attr_imp})
    mtpl.figure(figsize=(10,4))
    mtpl.bar(nmattr,attr_imp,color="#EB5406")
    mtpl.title("Feature Importance",fontsize=20,color="b")
    mtpl.xlabel("Features",fontsize=17,color="b")
    mtpl.ylabel("Importance",fontsize=17,color="b")
    mtpl.xticks(rotation=90)
    mtpl.grid()
    mtpl.show()
    return df_attr_sel

MD1=neural_network.MLPClassifier(hidden_layer_sizes=(100,2,), 
                                 activation='relu',
                                 solver='adam',
                                 batch_size='auto',
                                 learning_rate='adaptive',
                                 tol=0.00001,
                                 verbose=False,
                                 validation_fraction=0.2,
                                 max_iter=50)
MD2=neural_network.MLPClassifier(hidden_layer_sizes=(100,2,), 
                                 activation='tanh',
                                 solver='adam',
                                 batch_size='auto',
                                 learning_rate='adaptive',
                                 tol=0.00001,
                                 verbose=False,
                                 validation_fraction=0.2,
                                 max_iter=50)

AllMLP=[MD1,MD2]
MLPNms=["MLP_Relu","MLP_Tanh"]
MLP_PRC=[]
MLP_RCL=[]
MLP_FS=[]
MLP_ACR=[]
print("_____________________________________________________________________________")
for i in range(len(AllMLP)):
    print("                            {} ".format(MLPNms[i]))
    print("_____________________________________________________________________________")
    AllMLP[i].fit(X_train,y_train)
    prdIDD=AllMLP[i].predict(X_test)
    MLP_scr=round(sklearn.metrics.accuracy_score(y_test,prdIDD)*100,4)
    MLP_PRC.append(round(sklearn.metrics.precision_score(y_test, prdIDD, average='weighted')*100,4))
    MLP_RCL.append(round(sklearn.metrics.recall_score(y_test, prdIDD, average='weighted')*100,4))
    MLP_FS.append(round(sklearn.metrics.f1_score(y_test, prdIDD, average='weighted')*100,4))
    MLP_ACR.append(MLP_scr)
    cm=pandas.crosstab(y_test, prdIDD, rownames=['True'], colnames=['Predicted'], margins=True)
    print("\nAccuracy: {}%\n".format(round(MLP_scr,2)))
    print("\nClassification Report for {} \n\n{}".format(MLPNms[i],sklearn.metrics.classification_report(y_test, prdIDD)))
    print("\nConfusion Matrix for {} \n\n{}\n".format(MLPNms[i],cm.iloc[:6,:6]))
    print("_____________________________________________________________________________")

insh = idd_pred.shape[1]
oush= 2
ANN_Relu=tf.keras.Sequential()
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.InputLayer(input_shape=(insh,)))
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(100, activation='relu'))
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(100, activation='relu'))
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization())
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Flatten())
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.1))
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(512, activation='relu'))
ANN_Relu.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(oush, activation='softmax'))

ANN_Relu.summary()

ANN_Relu.compile(optimizer='adam', loss='sparse_categorical_crossentropy', metrics=['accuracy'])
batch_size = 32
epochs = 50
ANN_Relu_Hist = ANN_Relu.fit(X_trainnrm,y_trainnrm,epochs=epochs,verbose=1,validation_split=0.2)

insh = idd_pred.shape[1]
oush= 2
ANN_Tanh=tf.keras.Sequential()
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.InputLayer(input_shape=(insh,)))
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(100, activation='tanh'))
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(100, activation='tanh'))
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization())
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Flatten())
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.1))
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(512, activation='tanh'))
ANN_Tanh.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(oush, activation='softmax'))

ANN_Tanh.summary()

ANN_Tanh.compile(optimizer='adam', loss='sparse_categorical_crossentropy', metrics=['accuracy'])
batch_size = 32
epochs = 50
ANN_Tanh_Hist = ANN_Tanh.fit(X_trainnrm,y_trainnrm,epochs=epochs,verbose=1,validation_split=0.2)

lstst_Tanh,actst_Tanh=ANN_Tanh.evaluate(X_testnrm,y_testnrm)
lstrn_Tanh,actrn_Tanh=ANN_Tanh.evaluate(X_trainnrm,y_trainnrm)
